{"tid":1035103,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"台式珍珠奶 珍珠變曱甴","createTime":"2019-02-24T11:46:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-24T13:24:46.000Z","uid":72009,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"4255344c5e5ce272cfd873eff499b29426ca906e","tid":1035103,"uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-24T11:46:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20190224/640_2b598e837bf544fc04cf291b6128d408.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20190224%2F640_2b598e837bf544fc04cf291b6128d408.jpg&h=e81b0383&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n太噁心！高雄一名女網友今天臉書社團「爆廢公社」發文，自己到知名連鎖手搖飲料店買珍珠奶茶，想不到竟然「吸到蟑螂」，她po出的照片中蟑螂屍身已經殘破，讓網友直呼「太噁心」、「我要吐了」。<br />\n女網友未表明是在何處購買到這杯「蟑螂珍奶」，其他網友紛紛呼籲她快點公布店家，還有人則是留言「正喝著珍珠奶茶」、「太噁了吧！還不是全屍」、「嘎茲脆的」、「連蟑螂都喜歡的味道～」、「剛剛好想喝珍奶看到這個文章，你讓我省了一杯珍奶的錢」、「很正常喔！工作人員疏失忘記蓋蓋子」。還有人表示，「我爸也在同家連鎖飲料店（台中）喝到過」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20190224/1523030/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20190224%2F1523030%2F&d=NJeO18TDpfQgexRQIuB%2FGCL1bdbhbSvxCnYHZ8iA0HE%3D&h=1c05bfd0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20190224%2F1523030%2F&h=4aaae19b\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20190224/1523030/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20190224/640_2b598e837bf544fc04cf291b6128d408.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20190224%2F640_2b598e837bf544fc04cf291b6128d408.jpg&h=e81b0383&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76645728d2633d67340db5ed082e8ffd7281f701","tid":1035103,"uid":20066,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-24T11:49:12.000Z","msg":"做完gym都要飲返杯<br />\n補充蛋白質"},{"pid":"846c8faa0deb019d